		(uuid "be10eb27-c0f1-4915-808b-6e972a0eb188")
	)
	(text "Li-ion/LiFePO4 charge IC (TP4056 or MCP73831).\nUSB 5V input, single-cell output (3.0-4.2V Li-ion, 3.6V LiFePO4).\nCharge current set by PROG resistor (2k = 500mA for TP4056).\nCHG_STATUS: open-drain, active-low during charge.\nAdd reverse-blocking diode on VUSB if no USB-C CC logic.\nStatus LED: green=done, red=charging.\nInput cap: 4.7uF ceramic. Output cap: 4.7uF ceramic."
		(at 76.2 38.1 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.524 1.524)
			)
		)
